INNER JOIN [HH_USUARIO_HISTORIAL] AS [h] ON [p].[ID] = [h].[ID_PROYECTO]
WHERE [p].[FECHAEJECUCION] IS NOT NULL AND (DATEPART(year, [p].[FECHAEJECUCION]) = DATEPART(year, GETDATE()))
